dialogue.text: I fantasize travelling out of my living quarters, if only I had an opening...
Ohhh to sightsee Ahmerischa! To go see Francoise! To sell in Swisteria!
Ah, digging in my nogging won't help, seems I cant remember those darn countries.
What... H-HOW?? Didn't I obsess over them? Graaaaaah!!
